{"id": "1192989534372233216", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "387233801060876300", "author_name": "youfisi", "author_bot": false, "content": "话又说回来，抽卡在剧情上到底是个什么机制？", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T00:34:29.668000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1192989641247297566", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "387233801060876300", "author_name": "youfisi", "author_bot": false, "content": "每天给黑池发五次申请，「今天能给我派个唤醒体不」", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T00:34:55.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193021392443154442", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "流明之芯跟無垢之芯都是銀芯提純過後的產物，用於連結上位存在意志。", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T02:41:05.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193021717849845841", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "有沒有可能是通過讓黑池往銀芯內注入能量，同時也印上上位意志的印記，通過這樣來喚醒喚醒體？", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T02:42:22.807000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193043174063611955", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "先說玩家這邊的抽卡，玩家這邊的銀芯具有唯一抓取和無視距離直接抓取的特性，意味著玩家這邊的銀芯是可以直接在精神維度隨機抓取的，且無視精神維度的距離（正常來說就是從節點出發，要去抓取別的東西，抓到的時候，會距離節點很長一段路，這裡會出現2個問題，節點是否能被銀芯感知到和回去節點的能量是否足夠，當然因為是玩家這邊的銀芯，所以這2個問題不需要考慮，看到這裡你可能看不懂，說簡單點的，玩家的銀芯是直接傳送到抓取物品或是上位存在的地方，再傳送到節點，再將喚醒體復活並喚醒）", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T04:07:38.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["387233801060876300"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1192989534372233216", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
